==Summary==
===Spring Mini-Event===
* This year Spring 2018 Limited-time Operational Area Event will not take place. 
** However an Item Collection Mini-Event (similar to [[Mackerel|Saury Fishing]]) will be held instead.<ref name=tweetref6/><ref name=tweetref7/><ref name=tweetref8/>
** The Spring Mini-Event will be implemented in the a later Maintenance & Update and will not be included in the April 23rd Maintenance. 
*** The Spring Mini-Event will last until the Summer. 
===Summer 2018 Event===
* The next Limited-time Area Operation Event will be in [[Summer 2018 Event]]
**The Event will be '''Large'''<ref name=tweetref6/><ref name=tweetref7/><ref name=tweetref8/>
===New Ships/Remodels===
====Samuel B. Roberts====
*The American Destroyer Escort Samuel B. Roberts' Silhouette was revealed.
**She will be released on the April 23rd Update.
====Kagerou Kai Ni====
*{{ShipLink|Kagerou}} Kai Ni's Silhouette was revealed. 
**She is planned for release later soon.<ref name=tweetref6/><ref name=tweetref7/><ref name=tweetref8/>
***Multiple Kagerou-class Destroyers are planned to receive Kai Ni Remodels in the near future.
====Urakaze D Kai====
*{{ShipLink|Urakaze}}'s D Kai Remodel CG was revealed
**She will be released on the April 23rd Update. 
